♪ Hangin' low while I pop
a bottle off a yacht ♪

40:41.355 --> 40:43.649
♪ Chain swangin',
cling clang and it cost a lot ♪

40:43.691 --> 40:46.152
♪ I'm always after guala,
yeah, and you are not ♪

40:46.193 --> 40:48.696
♪ Bad... B, keep on goin' till
