40:52.408 --> 40:54.160
Zenzi.

40:54.201 --> 40:55.995
Lorraine fired me.

40:56.036 --> 40:58.706
I was the one that helped
Lino find Violet and...

40:58.747 --> 41:00.666
It's all my fault.

41:00.708 --> 41:02.042
I'm looking for Tom right now,

41:02.084 --> 41:04.086
but I haven't been able
to find him.

41:04.128 --> 41:06.172
♪ Bumpin' that Pac in the car,
pretendin' I got all the eyes ♪

41:06.213 --> 41:08.340
♪ On me, got a bad baby
