41:22.646 --> 41:23.814
Whoa! No!

41:23.856 --> 41:24.940
(electric zapping)
(grunting)

41:24.982 --> 41:26.775
What are you doing?! Ah!

41:26.817 --> 41:28.527
Get the watch!
TOM:
Let go of me. Ah!

41:28.569 --> 41:30.237
MAN:
Get the legs.

41:30.279 --> 41:32.114
(Tom grunting)

41:32.156 --> 41:34.950
(grunts, yelps)

41:34.992 --> 41:36.243
(panting)

